@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container mt-5">

    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">About Jallikattu GPS</h2>

    <p class="text-muted">
        Jallikattu GPS is a full-stack ASP.NET web application designed to
        centralize information and event management related to Jallikattu,
        a traditional cattle sport celebrated in Tamil Nadu.
        The platform helps users explore verified events, cattle breed
        information, and GPS-related products through a structured and
        easy-to-use interface.
    </p>

    <p class="text-muted">
        The application focuses on reliable data presentation and
        admin-moderated workflows, allowing users to submit events for
        approval while enabling administrators to manage content securely
        through a dedicated dashboard.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Key Features</h4>

    <ul class="text-muted">
        <li>Secure user registration and login system</li>
        <li>Role-based access control for Admin and Users</li>
        <li>Admin dashboard with complete CRUD operations</li>
        <li>Cattle breed management with images and detailed descriptions</li>
        <li>GPS product listings managed dynamically from the backend</li>
        <li>Event calendar displaying upcoming Jallikattu events</li>
        <li>Admin approval workflow for user-submitted events</li>
        <li>Cloud-hosted database with dynamic data loading</li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Technology Stack</h4>

    <ul class="text-muted">
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Razor Views</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> ASP.NET MVC, Entity Framework</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> SQL Server (Azure SQL)</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Session-based role management</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Hosting:</strong> Microsoft Azure App Services</li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Purpose of This Project</h4>

    <p class="text-muted">
        This project was developed to demonstrate end-to-end full-stack
        development skills, including database design, authentication and
        authorization, admin moderation workflows and cloud deployment on Microsoft Azure.
    </p>

</div>
